data.description: Ready to move in this beautiful house. Updated laminate floors, knockdown ceilings and walls, granite countertops, crown molding, recessed lights. Roof replaced in 2020. Spacious front porch where to enjoy the morning sun and the evenings socializing with friends. Located in Leisureville active-adult community with an endless amenities, friendly ambiance, and close to shopping areas, pristine beaches and easy access to highways and Airports.
